prompt: Anime-style illustration of a cute young female panda cub standing at the entrance of a magical bamboo forest path. The bamboo stalks are gently curved to form an archway, with sparkling rainbow-colored dewdrops on the leaves. Soft morning mist swirls around the scene. The style should be warm, whimsical, and child-friendly with soft lighting and pastel colors.
revised_prompt: Create an anime-style illustration of an adorable young female panda cub who is standing at the beginning of a magical path in a bamboo forest. The bamboo stalks curve naturally into an arch, with dewdrops that shimmer in all the colors of the rainbow resting on the leaves. The scene is enveloped in a soft morning mist. The mood of the image should evoke warmth, whimsy, and child-like wonder through the application of soft lighting and soothing pastel hues.
